OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMostly
OL,6,Fcloudy during Monday evening, with
OL,7,Fthis low enough to produce hill fog
OL,8,Fover the Moors and the odd spot of
OL,9,Fdrizzle. A few clearer spells emerging
OL,10,Finto the early hours of Tuesday. A
OL,11,Fwarm and rather muggy night.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FA few bright spells to start
OL,14,Fthe day, but cloud thickening again
OL,15,Ffrom the west with coastal and hill
OL,16,Ffog developing. Outbreaks of rain at
OL,17,Ftimes. Feeling humid.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
